    <string name="faq_title">Frequently Asked Questions</string>
    <string name="all_topics">All Topics</string>
    <string name="close_content_description">Close</string>
    <string name="faq_q1">What do I do if I forgot my password?</string>
    <string name="faq_a1">Go to \'Account\', tap the 3 dots in the top right, then Change password. We will send a code to your email to reset it.</string>
    <string name="faq_q2">How can I add a new parking lot?</string>
    <string name="faq_a2">Go to Parking Lots and tap the + button. Fill in all required details and click the \'Request Create Parking Lot\' button.</string>
    <string name="faq_q3">How do I disable a parking lot?</string>
    <string name="faq_a3">In My Parking Lots, select the parking lot, tap the 3 dots in the top right, then \'Disable Parking Lot\', confirm your action and that\'s it. Your parking lot will be hidden without losing its configuration.</string>
    <string name="faq_q4">Can I delete a parking lot?</string>
    <string name="faq_a4">No, but you can disable it. In My Parking Lots, select the parking lot, tap the 3 dots in the top right, then \'Disable Parking Lot\', confirm your action and that\'s it.</string>
    <string name="faq_q5">How do I withdraw my funds?</string>
    <string name="faq_a5">Go to Account > Wallet. Here you will see all your income, they go directly to your bank account and you can withdraw them whenever you want.</string>
    <string name="faq_q6">How do I edit a parking lot?</string>
    <string name="faq_a6">Open My Parking Lots, select the parking lot, tap the 3 dots in the top right, then \'Edit Parking Lot\'. Change the necessary data. Tap the \'Request Edit Parking Lot\' button.</string>
    <string name="faq_q7">Can I receive my funds in more than one account?</string>
    <string name="faq_a7">No, you can only register one account at a time in the application for now. You can change the bank account in Account > Wallet, click on the 3 dots and then \'Edit bank account\'.</string>
    <string name="faq_q8">How can I change my bank account?</string>
    <string name="faq_a8">Go to Account > Wallet > 3 dots > Edit bank account. Change the necessary data and tap the \'Edit bank account\' button.</string>
    <string name="faq_q9">Why would a parking lot be rejected?</string>
    <string name="faq_a9">This usually happens due to unclear photos, incomplete address, inconsistent data, or non-compliance with our policies (security, access, or legality). Correct and resubmit.</string>

